ologists, and sailing enthusiasts alike.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aCognitive stylesxPuluwat Atoll. 0aCognitive styleszPuluwat Atoll. 0aNavigationxPuluwat Atoll. 0aNavigationzPuluwat Atoll. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999z978311044221240uhttps://doi.org/10.4159/9780674037625zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780674037625423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780674037625/original  a978-3-11-044221-2  HUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999c1893d1999  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK